Additional Training Requirements

1. Data Engineering Training:

To gain expertise in building and managing scalable data pipelines, data integration, and storage systems.

Focus on tools and technologies like Apache Spark, Kafka, and advanced SQL for better data management and processing.



2. DevOps Training:

To deepen skills in automating infrastructure deployment, managing CI/CD pipelines, and improving system reliability.

Focus areas: Kubernetes, Docker, Jenkins, and cloud-native DevOps practices.




These trainings will help enhance technical proficiency, streamline processes, and align with organizational goals for automation and scalability.

